                           <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ አብርሐ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ትንሣኤ፡ ወአቡሁ፡ አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡…</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is written in the same hand as the main text. It mentions ʾabunä Wäldä ʾAbrǝha and his family and states that he donated the book to Tabotä Qǝddus Mikaʾel Śoṭa.
                        </item>
